text.text: Very simple kampung style mosque in Singapore.....plus this mosque is unique as it manages janazah management with fine details and reminds us that every soul will have to face demise and let's just pray that may Allah grant us heaven Insha Allah.....and visited graves of my cousin's grandpa and my grand aunt and I pray that may Allah forgives their shortcomings and grant them jannah.....
